rs, due to its high accuracy and excellent\nstability. \\texttt{kdeLF} is available at\n\\url{http://github.com/yuanzunli/kdeLF} with extensive documentation available\nat \\url{http://kdelf.readthedocs.org/en/latest~}.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sun, 13 Mar 2022 16:29:12 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-05-18"}
