nd 1,878,000 EV with a battery energy\nof 65 GWh and a DC charging power of 91 GW (12 GW AC) were operated in Germany\nby the end of 2022. The cumulative battery energy of about 72 GWh is therefore\nnearly twice the 39 GWh of nationally installed pumped hydro storage\ndemonstrating the enormous flexibility potential of battery storage for the\nenergy system.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sun, 13 Mar 2022 21:18:17 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 15 Mar 2022 08:16:59 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Thu, 23 Mar 2023 12:15:12 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-03-24"}
