 relative to the interplay of structural defects,\ntransport of solutes, thereby changing the resistance against crack\npropagation, which have been overlooked across the SCC literature and prevent\naccurate service life predictions.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 14 Mar 2022 12:53:46 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-08-24"}
