etic\ncalorimeters will ensure observation of the decays of dimuonium to\nelectron-positron pairs in presence of the Bhabba scattering background. An\nexpansion of the system to would extend the physics program of DIMUS to include\nprecision studies of rare processes with muons, pions, and $\\eta$ mesons\nproduced in $e^{+}e^{-}$ collisions.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 14 Mar 2022 14:39:23 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-03-15"}
