2$, compared to $V = 10$ for\nHARPS. We reach no clear conclusion about limb-dependent convective effects and\nthe possible confusion with DR; preliminary results suggest, however, that\nunder certain circumstances, while it seems that one effect could be mistaken\nfor the other, the accuracy of the fit (in particular of $\\alpha$) does not\nhold up under additional scrutiny.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 14 Mar 2022 14:50:19 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-05-25"}
