t coupling between moir\\'e trapped\nholes, and thus magnetic order can arise even in the dilute hole regime under\noptical excitation. This discovery adds a new and dynamic tuning knob to the\nrich many-body Hamiltonian of moir\\'e quantum matter.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 14 Mar 2022 15:02:49 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-05-04"}
